---
title: Beyond Meat® and Mushroom Spaghetti with Balsamic-Glazed Tomatoes
description: This dish is a perfect balance of savoury and sweet. Beyond Meat® and mushrooms make a rich, umami ragu, while bursting baby tomatoes and balsamic glaze add a bright pop of tangy sweetness.
